{"type": "article", "id": 32390, "title": "中国游客爱去澳大利亚，以及，Undercover与Supreme再度合作 | 浮华日报", "description": "我们为你挑选了今天最重要和最好看的时尚新闻。", "date": "2016-09-20T02:44:48Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 376, "name": "华尔街"}, {"id": 18636, "name": "贝嫂"}, {"id": 1231, "name": "PUMA"}, {"id": 1236, "name": "联合利华"}, {"id": 1331, "name": "雅诗兰黛"}, {"id": 1995, "name": "3.1 Phillip Lim"}, {"id": 10632, "name": "UNDERCOVER"}, {"id": 15798, "name": "NEIGHBORHOOD"}, {"id": 17463, "name": "老佛爷百货"}, {"id": 32840, "name": "Honest"}, {"id": 32951, "name": "Galeries Lafayette"}, {"id": 32952, "name": "Kohl’s"}, {"id": 32953, "name": "Seventh Generation"}], "category": 19, "column": 8, "author": 699895, "comment_count": 2, "praise_count": 27, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160920081027HrhPLi0nzbTVp8EC.jpg", "contents": "<h3>一些重要的新闻：</h3><p><b><a href=\"http://www.cpp-luxury.com/chinese-tourists-favor-the-u-s-and-australia-to-the-detriment-of-europe/\" rel=\"nofollow\">安全成为优先考虑因素，赴欧洲旅游的中国游客大幅减少</a> </b>| 今年八月，赴巴黎旅游的中国游客数下降了 5.7%，飞往巴黎的航班预订数则下降了 20%。澳大利亚正在成为中国游客的新目的地。&nbsp;<br></p><p><a href=\"http://wwd.com/business-news/financial/kohls-target-seasonal-hiring-69000-ecommerce-challenger-gray-christmas-10554126/\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>美国家庭百货公司 Kohl’s 计划新增 69000 名临时工</b></a> | 为了即将到来的年底忙季，Kohl’s 计划新增 69000 名临时工，这些工人将负责派发网络订单以及其他的工作。&nbsp;</p><p class=\"\"><b><a href=\"http://wwd.com/business-news/financial/wall-street-stocks-higher-amid-heightened-security-in-new-york-10553807/\" rel=\"nofollow\">纽约爆炸案之后，华尔街股价高开</a> </b>| 昨日，华尔街开始工作日，在安保加强的背景下华尔街股市上涨，开市后时尚和零售股价升高，投资者并没有因 Chelsea 爆炸而担惊受怕。其中，Fossil 集团的股价上涨了 3.5%，Coach 的股价上涨了 2.7%，J.C Penney 集团上涨了 3%，Michael Kors 则上涨了 2.7%。&nbsp;<br></p><p><a href=\"http://wwd.com/business-news/financial/unilever-seventh-generation-deal-takeover-honest-co-jessica-alba-10554816/\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>联合利华要收购 Seventh Generation</b></a> | 有消息称，联合利华对美国日化品牌 Seventh Generation 的收购已经进入最后阶段。这将会影响联合利华对 Honest 的收购。据联合利华所称，Seventh Generation 在去年的营业额为 2 亿美元，低于 Honest 的 3 亿美元。&nbsp;</p><h3>一些值得一看的：</h3><p><a href=\"http://hypebeast.cn/2016/9/neighborhood-2016\" rel=\"nofollow\">Neighborhood 发售 2016 秋冬新款</a>。包括多样化的牛仔外套、衬衫以及军装外套。还特别推出了与 Head Porter 联名的皮革配件。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160920083300KOmWZx12M40zgFah.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160920083300VXIaZRqu1kJ45Op8.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201609200833007TzBwZm3deSyFr9R.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160920083301dp3xec6fVEISkPHL.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160920083310zj3VuyvR5kOU41M6.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160920083312N27iK5b1qswXZvV9.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160920083313MYiy1znPK02CDm8N.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160920083314MYEIbo8j1ZQNhfCV.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160920083313lI6znAatMvujFmeo.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160920083316bY5ZzxksyjcOg0hX.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p><a href=\"http://hypebeast.cn/2016/9/undercover-x-supreme-2016-fw-collection\" rel=\"nofollow\">Undercover 与 Supreme 再度携手</a>，推出 2016 秋冬联名系列。该系列包括服装、小物，还有与 Dr.Martens 的三方联名鞋款。印有 Supreme 字样的 Gilapple 苹果灯成为了该系列的亮点。整个联名系列将于 9 月 22 日在纽约、洛杉矶和伦敦门店发售，24 日登陆日本。&nbsp;</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160920083126ZHG89aJi7emSpyEk.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666992\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160920083126m3rlkS0Pwi9q6A8c.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666016\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160920083126qoDJsOUGzvmlIkQx.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160920083126ycQNIJZ3zxKn5pS4.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160920083127fC79ZUvz6KYbtmpG.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666992\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160920083127JP0O8oLIxugiAXUv.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666992\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160920083151TdfshyLYeEziwRob.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666342\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160920083151v4sph7U3RSKQ6jFG.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666992\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160920083151OxDgnNQl06IoWVdP.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160920083237u5o1AVeaDtdLikOq.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160920083342vVhXARrjkOPSJ650.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p>时隔五年，PUMA 再度发售经典鞋款 Clyde 的全新周年纪念款 <a href=\"http://hypebeast.cn/2016/9/pumaclyde-wraith-pack\" rel=\"nofollow\">Clyde Wraith Pack</a>。这款鞋身使用了漆皮来增加质感，并搭配了奶油色的胶底，打造出一种高级奢华感。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160920083401LC5St4knphxmibcz.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160920083351esVaZWGDOU30k8KC.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160920083351qcD4Z3aioRfP1Bwy.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><p class=\"\">来看 Victoria Beckham SS17 春夏秀场上模特的妆容。秀场上的模特首次使用了 Victoria Beckham 与雅诗兰黛的合作款彩妆，以三款代表性的眼妆为重点，妆容简单清新。<a href=\"http://popbee.com/beauty/make-up/estee-lauder-victoria-beckham-ss-2017-makeup-collection/#\" rel=\"nofollow\">Victoria Beckham Estée Lauder 限量款彩妆</a>系列将于 10 月 15 日起正式发售。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160920083415gMUS1luK3n94ZmOv.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160920083425e84oyPWgnKhQwprI.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/2016092008342549GB20JV6IrcLedD.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160920083425m0dBPa8vGy9HMX31.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201609200834323WJozysMhRvwCjxn.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.665854\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160920083438MFpCvVYrkK5qZgLi.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160920083438Hkj3DRgaZst1rY8v.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p class=\"\">3.1 Phillip Lim 推出 ALIX 系列手袋新款。新的<a href=\"http://popbee.com/accessories/handbags/3-1-phillip-lim-fw16-alix-saddle-crossbody/\" rel=\"nofollow\"> ALIX Saddle Crossbody </a>共有五款配色，以柔软的小牛皮搭配标志性的金属万字扣，延续了一贯的简约风格。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201609200835376NMgudUe2VlsPb9H.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160920083559HrwOTCVJXuog9ZdN.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160920083605zlYhqtuvbB2I6fTF.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160920083605Tmbte3wO9WLncP4E.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160920083605y5ORl9MbwXIF7rVt.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201609200836125YwgvJdhicO4DIum.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160920083612CusTqVWivtXIkzOS.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>"}